<% layout('layouts/infoBoilerplate') -%>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900 to-gray-800 pt-20 pb-16 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div
            class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full opacity-10 bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/cubes.png')]">
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 text-center" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-4 tracking-tight">
                <i class="fas fa-car-crash text-[#fe424d] mr-3"></i> Host Insurance
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Peace of mind for every stay. Learn about Stayzio's
                comprehensive Host Protection Guarantee.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12">

            <div class="lg:w-1/4 hidden lg:block">
                <div
                    class="sticky top-28 bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl p-6 shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgb(0,0,0,0.04)]">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
                        <i class="fas fa-list text-[#fe424d]"></i> Contents
                    </h3>
                    <nav class="sticky-nav flex flex-col space-y-1">
                        <a href="#coverage"
                            class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-500 rounded-lg border-l-2 border-transparent hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">What's
                            Covered</a>
                        <a href="#exclusions"
                            class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-500 rounded-lg border-l-2 border-transparent hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">What's
                            Not Covered</a>
                        <a href="#claims"
                            class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-500 rounded-lg border-l-2 border-transparent hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">How
                            to File a Claim</a>
                    </nav>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="lg:w-3/4 prose-content bg-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgb(0,0,0,0.04)] border border-gray-100">

                <div id="coverage">
                    <h2><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> What is Covered?</h2>
                    <p>Stayzio's Host Protection Guarantee provides up to $1,000,000 in coverage in the rare event a
                        guest damages your property or belongings during a Stayzio stay.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Property Damage:</strong> Coverage for structural damage to your home caused by a
                            guest.</li>
                        <li><strong>Belongings:</strong> Protection for your personal property, furniture, and
                            electronics.</li>
                        <li><strong>Lost Income:</strong> Compensation for lost booking income if your property requires
                            repairs due to guest damage.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div id="exclusions">
                    <h2><i class="fas fa-times-circle"></i> What is Not Covered?</h2>
                    <p>While our guarantee is comprehensive, there are certain exclusions you should be aware of:</p>
                    <div class="highlight-box">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> Important Exclusions</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Cash, securities, or rare collectibles.</li>
                            <li>Damage caused by normal wear and tear over time.</li>
                            <li>Bodily injury or property damage to third parties (this may be covered under separate
                                Host Liability Insurance).</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="claims">
                    <h2><i class="fas fa-file-signature"></i> How to File a Claim</h2>
                    <p>If you discover damage after a guest checks out, follow these steps immediately:</p>
                    <ol>
                        <li>Take clear photos or videos of the damage as evidence.</li>
                        <li>Message the guest through the Stayzio platform to notify them of the issue and try to
                            resolve it directly.</li>
                        <li>If the guest refuses to pay, submit an official claim through your Host Dashboard within 14
                            days of checkout.</li>
                        <li>Provide any requested documentation, such as repair estimates or original receipts.</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>